* Sends bulk SMS results after the race is finalized.
* When to use:      After all errors are fixed and "Event to Database" has been run.
* How to use:       Double-click to blast results to all runners with a PHONE and TIME.
* Note:             Keep messages under 160 characters. Total length depends on URL size.
* Setup:            Ensure "Event to Database" is run first to populate result fields.

/* Before running: You MUST execute the "Event to Database" command. 
* This copies Finish Times and Places into the participant records so 
* this script can find them.
*/

Select              PHONE
NE
And
Select              TIME
NE

SMS Destination     PHONE
No Column Headers
No Page Numbers
No Total
Squeeze

* Message Construction
Field               Name
Message             : Time:
Space               1
Field               TIME
Message             . Div:
Space               1
Field               DIVPLACE
Message             /
Field               DIVTOTAL
Message             . Full Results:
Space               1
Field               Result URL

